dct_description_sm: Map shows pre World War I international boundaries, independendent and dependent states administrative boundaries. Sea routes distance travel are indicated, railways are shown. Inset maps: "Asia mineure, Égypte, Arabie, etc." Scale 1:17,500,00 -- [northern Europe]. Scale 1:13,000,000 Prime meridians: Greenwich and Paris.
